page.title: 14HOMELIFE TYPICAL DAY
page.content: When I am at home on a Saturday I like to get up about nine and have a breakfast of Corn Flakes and milk.After breakfast I go out and because I live on a farm I have lots of places to go.I usually go to the wood and back and I pretend I am riding a pony on a funny shaped tree. When I come back to the house I watch a programme called {Number 73}mostly and after that I go to listen to the radio.I like listening to {Radio 1} until dinner time.For dinner we have a pie and potatoes and after dinner I go to take the dogs for a walk.After tea I may go for a ride on my bike.After supper I watch television and at about nine o'clock I go to bed.
